Keyterms to Note: 
- [Forward Bias](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%E2%80%93n_junction): Direction of easy current flow
- [Reverse Bias](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%E2%80%93n_junction): Direction of little or no currrent flow

